# Capture and condense survey

This is the map of the observer capture and condense loop as it is running on flagg on 2026-07-17.

Verdicts use the review brief vocabulary: `working`, `wobbly`, `gap`.

## Current deployment

**Verdict: wobbly.** The live loop is running, but the dev checkout and release checkout are not on the same commit.

What runs:

- `com.joelclaw.observer-tick` runs `/Users/joel/.joelclaw/bin/observer-tick.sh` every 1800 seconds. Receipt: `~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.joelclaw.observer-tick.plist` has `StartInterval` `1800`, `StandardOutPath` `/tmp/observer-tick.log`, and `StandardErrorPath` `/tmp/observer-tick.log`.
- `com.joelclaw.observer-dream` runs `/Users/joel/.joelclaw/bin/observer-dream.sh` daily at 06:10 local. Receipt: `~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.joelclaw.observer-dream.plist` has `StartCalendarInterval` hour `6`, minute `10`, and logs to `/tmp/observer-dream.log`.
- `com.joelclaw.observer-neat-memory` runs `/Users/joel/.joelclaw/observer-release/bin/neat-memory.sh` daily at 16:15 local. Receipt: `~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.joelclaw.observer-neat-memory.plist` has `StartCalendarInterval` hour `16`, minute `15`, and logs to `/tmp/observer-neat-memory.log`.
- `launchctl list | grep -i observ` returned all three labels with last status `0`: `com.joelclaw.observer-tick`, `com.joelclaw.observer-dream`, `com.joelclaw.observer-neat-memory`.

State lives here:

